track.name: Voulez-Vous
comments: I 1979 this song reached number 3 as part of a double  A sided single along with the superior Angel Eyes.However it was a great package and this song still stands the test of time.Amazingly ABBA didn't have one number 1 back in 1979 just several top 10 hits.
In 1979 i wasn't even born. La question c'est, Voulez-Vous ?

In 1979 I was 17 going on 18 and in love with Janet, Patricia, Janet, Julie, Sally, Gill, Sue, Judy, Anne, Carol, Wendy, Ruth (ah Ruth I should have married Ruth).  I remember them all and its great to give them all the credit they were and hopefully are still the best things in my memories of love and all things emotional.

My Children are Sally & Suzanne there names were influenced by my loves.
